308
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:46,391
- No, no, no.
- Just give me one minute, okay?

309
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,949
The flubber is placed
in my back pocket.

310
00:24:51,040 --> 00:24:53,713
When I exit this window,
I will fall to the ground.

311
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:58,749
When I hit the ground, the flubber will
send me right back up unharmed. Watch.

312
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:08,914
- Ta-ta, my love.
- Are you nuts?

313
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:12,476
- I`ll be right back.
- Phillip!

314
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,953
Ah!

315
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:19,876
- Ouch.
- Phillip, are you hurt?

316
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,991
