317
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:25,629
Well, if you think that
you are going to get my sympathy,
you are wasting your time.

318
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:28,479
Ooh! We are finished!

319
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:32,713
Sara.

320
00:25:32,800 --> 00:25:35,712
Oh!

