323
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,277
Dad?

324
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:09,832
Somebody in your organization
screwed up big time.

325
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:12,115
I got thrown off
the basketball team.

326
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:17,638
