00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:29,799
I`m very sorry!

438
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:33,356
Hang on, Weebo!
Oh! Ha, ha, ha! Oh!

439
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:36,750
Whoa! Oh! Oh, Weebo!

