00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,751
Whoa!

442
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:49,312
Oh!

443
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,637
Oh! Yes!

444
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:02,515
Oh, Weebo. Come on up.

445
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:04,955
Please. You`ve gotta see this.

446
00:35:06,200 --> 00:35:09,397
