456
00:35:51,120 --> 00:35:53,111
Abandon ship!

457
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:58,029
Oh!

458
00:35:58,120 --> 00:36:00,111
Yes!

459
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,837
